	<section id="Blue_River">
	

		<br/><br/><br/>
		<h3>Blue River</h3>
		<p>It's coming on Christmas, they're cutting down trees<br/>
		They're putting up reindeer and singing songs of joy and peace<br/>
		I wish I had a river I could skate away on<br/>
		Oh oh oh oh I made my baby cry<br/>
		I wish I had a river</p>
		<p>When those white snow flakes start falling<br/>
		I'll hear my blue, blue memory a-calling<br/>
		You'll be doing alright with your Christmas of white<br/>
		But I'll have a blue, blue blue blue Christmas</p>

		<br/><br/><br/>

	</section>

	<hr/>

	<section id="Sweet_Something">
		<br/><br/><br/>
		<h3>Sweet Something</h3>
		<p>Sweet Peggy Sue<br/>
		She never wanted nobody<br/>
		To feel blue<br/>
		Or write a song<p/>

		<p>What do you do<br/>
		When you're not after his money<br/>
		Oh and the choir won't quit humming 'girl get along'?</p>

		<p><b>Country singer doesn't know how to let go<br/>
		Of the river that floods his words<br/>
		Take one hard good look at me and you'll know<br/>
		That I never have trouble being heard</b></p>

		<p>Sweet Mary Jane</br>
		She left that boy down on the corner</br>
		Clutching his crutches</br>
		With shaking hands</p>

		<p>Who do you blame</br>
		For all the highs the lows the rushes</br>
		All of the good times wasting good time that you can stand?</p>

		<p><b>Some people never learn how to let go</br>
		Of the threads they're hanging on</br>
		Take one hard good look at me and you'll know</br>
		That I've never I've never I've never I've never been wrong</b></p>

		<p>Sweet Lady Life</br>
		Oh we've been dancing for a long time </br>
		On the edge of this knife</br>
		In the back of a girl</p>

		<p>I wonder why</br>
		For all our twisting and our jiving</br>
		She's still standing she's still smiling her hair's still curled</br>

		<p><b>Some people really know how to let go</br>
		Of the chains that hold them down</br>
		Take one hard good look at me and you'll know</br>
		That this face it ain't never known a frown</b></p>

		<br/><br/><br/>
	</section>
	<hr/>
	<section id="Runaway_Heart">

		<br/><br/><br/>
		<h3>Runaway Heart</h3>
		<p><b>CHORUS<br/>
		Got a runaway heart<br/>
		Got a runaway heart<br/>
		Runaway-ay-ay</p></b>
	
		<p>Never known a love lost<br/>
		Faster than I lost yours<br/>
		My heart left my body that's the cost<br/>
		Wearing a lifetime of lovin' reward</p>

		<p><b>CHORUS</b></p>

		<p>I started chasing it chasing you<br/>
		Catching all the blood I could save<br/>
		I swear someday we'll meet until then it won't rest a beat<br/>
		It's sustained by the song of a slave</p>

		<p>And if you keep picking it'll never heel/heal<br/>
		Oh if you kep picking it'll never heel/heal<br/>
		If you keep picking it'll never heel/heal<br/>
		If you keep picking it'll never heel/heal</p>

		<p><b>CHORUS</b></p>
		<br/><br/><br/>

	</section>

